country-block (0.4.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Stop applying firewall rules automatically during package install or
    upgrade.
  * Split data refresh from firewall application with the new sync command.
  * Add country-block status for read-only consistency checks.
  * Add country-block clear for removing live managed firewall rules.
  * Allow country-block try to test the current rules file by default.
  * Rename config.conf to rules.conf.
  * Install systemd units disabled and stopped by default.
  * Warn users when boot restore or weekly updates are not enabled.

